{"tid":1960990,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"乜做老細可以唔咁冇誠信，如果我一早知你翻新係炒左我，我一早就搵左工啦！！！","createTime":"2020-04-06T13:02:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-06T16:04:43.000Z","uid":288714,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f32d75a68d10308837fdb5bc9227a75251c075d1","tid":1960990,"uid":288714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T13:02:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4UY1xkL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4UY1xkL.jpg&h=fecd02e3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ps1Ku7t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPs1Ku7t.jpg&h=7d44f762&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yzbOckP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyzbOckP.jpg&h=a135ae0d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nkz8ckR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnkz8ckR.jpg&h=54f39cf1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q5TEi0S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq5TEi0S.jpg&h=78807744&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">乜做老細可以唔咁冇誠信，如果我一早知你翻新係炒左我，我一早就搵左工啦！！！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就係你話唔炒人，我先繼續做，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">做左幾年野，剛剛先儲夠錢搬出黎住，而家叫我點交租</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n//<br />\n<br />\n本會收到同業資料指香港洲際酒店曾於2017 年6月20號向員工宣佈2019年初將會局部進行酒店翻新工程，為期12-16個月，強調所有員工均不會被解僱；此計劃於2018年3月14日宣佈將延遲一年至本年度初，並再次承諾於工作期間將繼續雇用所有員工。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n為加強員工信心，酒店方面更向員工發出「翻新期間工作安排意向書」，讓員工選擇放假、調部門、其他培訓安排，員工因此曾經深感滿意，願意留低繼續為酒店服務。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可惜事與願違，酒店方面出爾反爾，於早前宣佈遣散幾乎所有員工，令逾數百名員工頓時手足無措。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本會在此呼籲香港洲際酒店老闆吳繼煒先生，就他旗下之酒店所作所為作回應。同時歡迎其屬下的公司同事「盡訴心中情」，直接在老闆上提出問題/表達個人意見。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n意見收集處：<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfuXsCg6wbhDQwjSdIqthvvHKS9ABvib8aYrkF206symJq0sQ/viewform?usp=pp_url\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSfuXsCg6wbhDQwjSdIqthvvHKS9ABvib8aYrkF206symJq0sQ%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dpp_url&d=IFfiXVp8wSeEFxWCfbiPLdMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=e9a3f422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfuXsCg6wbhDQwjSdIqthvvHKS9ABvib8aYrkF206symJq0sQ/viewform?usp=pp_url</a><br />\n<br />\n//<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">其實係係工會page睇到呢個po，先發現自己比人呃左</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82d918eb816bede8711fb00929237508245eecfc","tid":1960990,"uid":103102,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T13:04:37.000Z","msg":"有錢佬都係仆街黎"},{"pid":"0c4b6fabff6258e3f566d0f2e48c37b0821c5742","tid":1960990,"uid":58896,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T13:17:37.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n呢間嘢呃9人<br />\n俾假希望<br />\n簽好唒agreement <br />\n點知到頭來變condom <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：受害人"},{"pid":"c7b61fe9cda1707d9674f0f35c29f03e9d31697e","tid":1960990,"uid":68939,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T13:18:06.000Z","msg":"好撚賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依個時勢叫人點搵工"},{"pid":"d88392ea0ce05d10e5ba0dbe27157e8d174c78e3","tid":1960990,"uid":255637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T13:20:07.000Z","msg":"的確係賤既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e39d227933a4a6d3176ad9318eb3a4cb8c0bf8dc","tid":1960990,"uid":67412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T13:20:56.000Z","msg":"正仆街! 出爾反爾! 如果知道點都係要走， 好景嗰陣一早唔會做你呢間酒店啦!<br />\n利申:其他酒店人"},{"pid":"d1bfe85a3180f0d55e97a8f13e0a0b7c61e322ac","tid":1960990,"uid":181318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T13:23:16.000Z","msg":"好仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92cf8e4be06cc0a1cc5420228b746df1d9948e29","tid":1960990,"uid":58896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T13:23:38.000Z","msg":"17年簽落協議<br />\n等到今日<br />\n點知乜都無<br />\n我人生有幾多個3年俾呢條仆街浪費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db77f7ec9e194228e749e577fd5a5a5f504dc9fc","tid":1960990,"uid":288714,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T13:25:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">本來傾好晒，都冇諗過會咁，以為最多冇花紅啫，點知而家⋯⋯⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一出嚟做嘢就做酒店，而家真係唔知可以做咩好</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a3847eb4718729e04d398125e5283e78f7457e2","tid":1960990,"uid":22108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T13:30:57.000Z","msg":"呢個時候係難搵工小小<br />\n加油呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b33f26d3774e35a79ada708c49eff5aceb0fc9d","tid":1960990,"uid":88599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T13:31:31.000Z","msg":"洲際員工變哂condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b86e2f82178570fbc4d388ae608b6d6b111c43dc","tid":1960990,"uid":178398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T13:32:54.000Z","msg":"咁包皮既時期仲呃鳩人 屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b13c31f075d2d435f15f1611b081973850686074","tid":1960990,"uid":266598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T13:42:26.000Z","msg":"係怕開左頭，愈來愈多酒店會咁仆街"},{"pid":"29ac2285110a6ce9e5f8453ef603b3b5b936d3e0","tid":1960990,"uid":193208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T13:59:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2463fb8f5169e8aaf682bc764b0d81a8127bca5a","tid":1960990,"uid":345733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T15:07:58.000Z","msg":"都唔止一間 今日百樂都話裝修啦 間間酒店都當員工condom 今年又話社會動盪冇生意喇 花紅要派少啲啦 共渡時艱喇 轉個頭又話疫